title: Lineage II Chronicle 5 [SupremeL2 Server Version] [supremel2.com
description:
This is the Lineage II client that you need in order to play on the Supreme L2 server. The server itself can be found at http://supremel2.com/ This is an Lineage II Chronicle 5 version, fully updated for playing at the Supreme L2 Server.

Instructions for installing:

1: Unzip with WinRar or something else.
2: Go into the "system" folder of the game.
3: Make an account at http://supremel2.com/
4: Run the file sl2.exe, play and have fun!

REMEMBER: DO NOT RUN THE l2.exe BECAUSE THIS IS THE LAUNCHER TO THE OFFICIAL SERVER AND THE AUTOUPDATER WILL RUIN YOUR SUPREMEL2 VERSION OF THE GAME!
